snippet.title: FIFA 15 Ultimate Team Mobile - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
CHOOSE YOUR STYLE. CREATE YOUR TEAM. PLAY TO WIN. 

Experience the excitement of managing and playing the world's best football players, anytime, anywhere.

FIFA 15 Ultimate Team is available for free download on Apple App Store®, Google Play®, and Windows Phone® : http://bit.ly/YTFUT15
